Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:23.09,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}激情 干渴若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.82,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}阖上双目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:29.39,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}罪孽深重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:32.27,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:43.24,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你的气味 令人发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:47.26,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}真夜中醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:50.41,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}疯狂 爱 一并饮干
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:53.44,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}投入这臂弯中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:56.60,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}"那边的黑暗是苦涩的"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:02:02.37,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你惶然不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:06.00,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}即将要迎来永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:09.25,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}"这边的黑暗是甜美的"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:15.47,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}我深深地刺入
